<h2 style="text-align: left;">Save £100pp on your lift pass &amp; ski hire</h2>
<p><strong>Save £100pp*</strong> on your <a data-udi="umb://document/500f33ac6e5a40b7900b12234eb39470" href="/{localLink:umb://document/500f33ac6e5a40b7900b12234eb39470}" title="Next Winter">2024/25 ski holiday</a> when you pre-buy your lift pass and equipment hire/carriage.</p>
<p>The offer is valid across all European destinations (excluding holidays to Canada and Lapland) and is valid on all departure dates between 1st December 2024 and 30th April 2025. The offer ends on the Monday 3rd June 2024.</p>
<p>Buy any lift pass (<em>found within the 'Extras' tab on checkout</em>) and add either ski/snowboard hire or ski/snowboard carriage at the same time, for the same person to receive the discount.</p>
