<h2>Travel with confidence</h2>
<p>We make booking your ski or snowboarding trip straight forward - All of our ski holidays <strong>include your flights, transfers and accommodation</strong>. Our holidays are also <strong>ABTA/ATOL protected</strong> and with over <strong>85 years of experience</strong>, you can trust us to deliver your perfect holiday.</p>
<p><img src="/media/13095389/inghams-in-safe-hands-charcoal.png" alt="safehands" data-udi="umb://media/afba17a916e84fcc848acce5dda4f9c4" /></p>
<h2>Terms &amp; conditions</h2>
<ul>
<li>Buy any lift pass and add either ski/snowboard hire or ski/snowboard carriage at the same time and for the same person to receive the discount.</li>
<li>To add on ski/snowboard carriage and claim £100 discount, you must call our reservations team to book. This will not automatically apply on our website.</li>
<li>Valid on all destinations, excluding Canada and Lapland.</li>
<li>Valid on all departure dates between 1st December 2024 and 30th April 2025.</li>
<li>The offer can be added at any time during the offer period, as long as both items are added together.</li>
<li>The offer will be available to select during the booking process – select the items you require, and the discount will automatically apply if eligible.</li>
<li>This offer can also be added post booking, via MyBooking or by calling our reservations team.</li>
<li>This offer can be used in conjunction with other offers, except where offers/packages/bundles also contain a lift pass.</li>
</ul>
</div>
